Package: anvil
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, build-essential
Description: Fast C build system with watch mode
 Anvil is a lightweight, fast build system for C projects that generates
 Makefiles from simple configuration files. Features include:
 .
  * Simple configuration syntax
  * Automatic source file discovery with wildcards
  * Watch mode for automatic rebuilds
  * Colored output for better readability
  * Cross-platform support